channel.title: Uncalled Attack v3 - Beasting With DSPK
channel.description: [center][img]http://img813.imageshack.us/img813/7645/ua7g.jpg[/img][/center] Hey guys! I'm working on a new project and I'm beasting it up with a DSPK source. I'm going to have many of features, more then what I've already added, and will add and fix more minigames. The project, so far, is going great and I will continue to keep this topic updated. I may release this project whenever I'm finished with it. All the skills will be rewritten because Project Insanity skills are just awful. Whenever that's done, minigames will be worked on, so on and so forth. You guys get the point; but this is going to be a huge project, the best and biggest Uncalled Attack I've ever had. I can't wait to see the outcome of it, you guys can't wait until I release this. But there's no promises that I will actually release it, but there's a pretty decent chance I will since I haven't released any good sources on MoparScape, and I need to. [hr] [b]Goals:[/b] Green = Completed Orange = Working on Red = Haven't started ---------------------------------------------------- -Clipped Following -Kalphite Queen -Bones To Bananas -Bones To Peaches -Castle Wars -Better Skills -In game Highscores -Highscores -Level 99 Skill Rewards -Critical Hits -Vote Rewards -Jad Minigame -Automated Donation System -Fix Over Powered Leeches -Add Cities and Accessories -Overloads -NPC Clipping -Barbarian Assault -Fix Memory Leak -Summoning -Firemaking More will be coming. [hr] [b]Images:[/b] [img]http://i1095.photobucket.com/albums/i480/uncalled1/newua1.gif[/img] [img]http://i1095.photobucket.com/albums/i480/uncalled1/ua5-1.gif[/img] [img]http://i1095.photobucket.com/albums/i480/uncalled1/ua6.gif[/img] [img]http://i1095.photobucket.com/albums/i480/uncalled1/ua4.gif[/img] [img]http://i1095.photobucket.com/albums/i480/uncalled1/ua8.gif[/img] [img]http://i1095.photobucket.com/albums/i480/uncalled1/ua-sum.gif[/img] [img]http://i1136.photobucket.com/albums/n484/uncalled/HP-Rewards.gif[/img] [img]http://i1095.photobucket.com/albums/i480/uncalled1/ua2.jpg[/img][img]http://i1095.photobucket.com/albums/i480/uncalled1/ua3.jpg[/img] [img]http://img824.imageshack.us/img824/2434/uaimg1.jpg[/img][img]http://img845.imageshack.us/img845/6467/uaimg2.jpg[/img] [hr] Gimmiez feehd bak pleaze. :) <3
